<paragraph id="8D19AB59320CFFF45CCF0568FC6AFA49" blockId="2.[166,1224,1232,1419]" pageId="2" pageNumber="403">
D i a g n o s t i c c h a r a c t e r s. Eyes hairy; third antennal segment orange, darkened above and shorter than 2.5 times as long as second segment; frons broad and convex; face without distinct hairs (microtrichia not taken into account) (
<figureCitation id="159DB7DC320CFFF45F7A0528FC5DFAA9" box="[878,937,1361,1387]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="3.[170,203,1674,1696]" captionTargetBox="[176,1228,642,1642]" captionTargetId="figure-285@3.[170,1229,636,1646]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Fig. 1. Cheilosia aerea (a–c): a — dorsal view of female, b — lateral view of head of female, c — male genitalia; C. cumanica (d–f): d — dorsal view of female, e — frontal view of head of female, f — male genitalia; C. lola, female (g–h): g — dorsal view, h — frontal view of head. Рис. 1. Cheilosia aerea (a–c): a — самка, вид сверху; b — голова самки, латеральный вид, c — гениталии самца; C. cumanica (d–f): d — самка, вид сверху, e — голова самки, фронтальный вид, f — гениталии самца; C. lola, самка (g–h): g — вид сверху, h — голова, фронтальный вид." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6449151" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6449151/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="403">fig. 1</figureCitation>
, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320CFFF45FA30528FC37FAA8" box="[951,963,1361,1386]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="403">e</emphasis>
); at least first segment of mid tarsus or bases of tibiae yellowish; genitalia as in (
<figureCitation id="159DB7DC320CFFF45F290508FC8CFA49" box="[829,888,1393,1419]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="3.[170,203,1674,1696]" captionTargetBox="[176,1228,642,1642]" captionTargetId="figure-285@3.[170,1229,636,1646]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Fig. 1. Cheilosia aerea (a–c): a — dorsal view of female, b — lateral view of head of female, c — male genitalia; C. cumanica (d–f): d — dorsal view of female, e — frontal view of head of female, f — male genitalia; C. lola, female (g–h): g — dorsal view, h — frontal view of head. Рис. 1. Cheilosia aerea (a–c): a — самка, вид сверху; b — голова самки, латеральный вид, c — гениталии самца; C. cumanica (d–f): d — самка, вид сверху, e — голова самки, фронтальный вид, f — гениталии самца; C. lola, самка (g–h): g — вид сверху, h — голова, фронтальный вид." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6449151" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6449151/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="403">fig. 1</figureCitation>
, 
<emphasis id="BFD2774B320CFFF45F910508FC79FA49" box="[901,909,1393,1419]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="403">f</emphasis>
